{"tid":1639341,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門女校學生妹：「多謝各位屯門牛同校友今日嘅支持！」","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:36:16.000Z","uid":67440,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e6149f48b191fd3ad592c9fc53e2c4dc9342777b","tid":1639341,"uid":67440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打大家好，首先我哋真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>好多謝好多謝大家響應我哋嘅號召</strong></span></span>，我哋知道我地訂個日子係今日係比較倉促，所以我哋真係好擔心唔會有人嚟，但到最後都見到各位嘅出現，我哋嘅士氣都有所增加！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然今日嚟聲援嘅人數唔算多，但已經遠超我預期，尤其係見到一啲已經畢咗業好多年嘅師姐都返嚟支持我地，我真係好感動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地之後都一定會再有活動，亦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔會因遇到困難而就此退縮，會繼續去爭取屬於我哋嘅自由與民主</strong></span></span>，所以希望各位巴打絲打繼續支持我哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，我想同今日喺劉金龍門口派口罩嘅嗰位男同學講聲多謝，我估唔到得你一個男仔你都敢過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好多謝你，亦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>好多謝今日有嚟聲援我地嘅巴打絲打！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，校長今日亦就呢件事作出咗回應。<br />\n<br />\n一，學校一直都係保持<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中立</strong></span></span>嘅態度。<br />\n<br />\n二，校方<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>尊重每一位同學</strong></span></span>嘅立場同睇，但同時我哋亦應<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>包容唔同持份者嘅意見</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n三，校長絕對<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>歡迎學生親自去揾佢傾談</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n四，學校並<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無打壓學生</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n五，學校係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">畀學生戴口罩返學</span></strong></span>，並且<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔會作出記名等行為</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n以上五點為我哋得知嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大約重點</strong></span></span>，如果有任何補充，希望各位<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>師姐師妹可以幫幫手</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我哋有校友就呢件事整咗份聯署，我哋希望各位可以再幫個忙，感激不盡！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdr4OFtvpj9E1vMHbdiw4J_nOy5AMBPvM47YM9o7NR3PaiAtA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdr4OFtvpj9E1vMHbdiw4J_nOy5AMBPvM47YM9o7NR3PaiAtA%2Fviewform&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=2169a007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdr4OFtvpj9E1vMHbdiw4J_nOy5AMBPvM47YM9o7NR3PaiAtA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631203</a>"},{"pid":"a87baf95ec41d71aebac779da0024d1128124ccb","tid":1639341,"uid":67440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609418eab7c14b7758b2ad64cc771acb2312db7d","tid":1639341,"uid":283861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae7f88b24a9c8b22feec0e7621ff636aee246283","tid":1639341,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b6258f0504e265f0d4d1e8652f96f1cc5a8391","tid":1639341,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"屯門好似得一間女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8005cd2c7be7adec454f30d85074bba433c349f0","tid":1639341,"uid":72425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"我都有嚟㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫學生妹推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6072f1b6bdcbff43a6d567f909eec9fcccf06c26","tid":1639341,"uid":67440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e3ac73817deb145bc2ac39f44a997d71aedd91","tid":1639341,"uid":47112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"35b6258f0504e265f0d4d1e8652f96f1cc5a8391","tid":1639341,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"屯門好似得一間女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"正想講<br />\n認真以前識一兩個學生都係好鬼有霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d52b2ea294a9148bddb1fd56291352fffc20226","tid":1639341,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"支持學生<span style=\"font-size: small;\">妹</span>"},{"pid":"7fa8c2adcce5aa6d2953e60e53ce57e59edf11b2","tid":1639341,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b685d820ee90085791166c8e7bd16d3955ade4e","tid":1639341,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"學生妹出到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連仔梗係幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373f2ff037d023d31439cf223201cb34d6c24b3e","tid":1639341,"uid":331546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"但係仲有一件事希望大家可以留意<br />\n就係校長完全冇回應過關於之前嗰位鄭老師件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我希望校方可以跟進呢件事<br />\n<br />\n利申 校友"},{"pid":"a047fcbd5ee3e29681c8c1b26241e16a226981a6","tid":1639341,"uid":147972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"學生妹加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c46f4f594fabcc70f8a99ba7269a9e47172f43","tid":1639341,"uid":67440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"仲有一件<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好重要嘅事</strong></span></span>，就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>校長佢並無回應到「『藍』老師事件」</strong></span></span>！！我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔希望呢件事就此會畀人淡忘</strong></span></span>！！各位一定要幫手推！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門女校「藍」老師   「禁蒙面法」實施後竟立刻表示：「我期待咗好耐」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631203</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8782c064eef55b31cfa5a08fb9ffc1f31668d776","tid":1639341,"uid":209552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日校方並未就「藍老師」一事作出回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15071f2c3ccc68b50bdb1216be21be8267c77bad","tid":1639341,"uid":147972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"bec8cad788facb8e0aa42293cb1b32e544d35506","tid":1639341,"uid":72425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7722263c309982fe08e83dcc715ad2175da7264d","tid":1639341,"uid":67440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c30a90c637c17d7755fa9f8e13c35d021593fd","tid":1639341,"uid":67440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfce1c35a3471d016a99c7955c4d3097eb2138ed","tid":1639341,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"想識學生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90986e754c4548ca1b1983f05d28cad13f4f2d0d","tid":1639341,"uid":227337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:43:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72d3998cdba615abef15f7ee5891c9d16a829591","tid":1639341,"uid":320636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90986e754c4548ca1b1983f05d28cad13f4f2d0d","tid":1639341,"uid":227337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:43:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"巴打想要咩圖？"},{"pid":"ae43baf04bde8f671d82d31359b2c8a70aa6a57a","tid":1639341,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b6258f0504e265f0d4d1e8652f96f1cc5a8391","tid":1639341,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"屯門好似得一間女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067948dbac51870f80308a606ec042f03572dbd7","tid":1639341,"uid":142590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"劉金龍都有唔少腥移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb30c23f34831d9f43c27b45b87533a286eea9e","tid":1639341,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"067948dbac51870f80308a606ec042f03572dbd7","tid":1639341,"uid":142590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"劉金龍都有唔少腥移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"不嬲都多，但以前好多腥移民同學都有轉化成真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}